{"tid":2013189,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"念念不忘612","createTime":"2020-05-12T06:50:49.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-12T05:32:12.000Z","uid":302364,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"8f1a1b1a4fd00f5affc7baab78e50f97abf338d7","tid":2013189,"uid":302364,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T06:50:49.000Z","msg":"仲有一個月就612一週年。<br />\n你......仲記唔記得當晚嘅初心？小弟改咗Juno 首<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">念念不忘</span></strong>，希望可以keep 到大家抗爭嗰團火啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">念念不忘 612</span></span><br />\n</span><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">十年又過去 今天重踏這裡<br />\n記得那晚萬人共聚 變動似水<br />\n在這邊堵塞過馬路吧 那邊高唱過Hallelujah<br />\n記起了 往事壯麗如畫<br />\n<br />\n仍舊記著初心嗎 不甘昨日舊回憶幻化<br />\n你記得這感動嗎 最美那青春開着花<br />\n<br />\n這晚民主會結束 審議過後便會安葬<br />\n教我們賭上血肉之軀 拯救這個海港<br />\n若有神請你降福 保守我家一切平安<br />\n縱使賭注太大 未來茫茫<br />\n至少今晚會用盡氣 抵抗<br />\n<br />\n但時代變化 怎麼隨便變卦<br />\n你怎會最後仍認命 說為養家<br />\n就去專心工作幹活吧 再不敢去說罷工開花<br />\n你這叫 變做了大人嗎<br />\n<br />\n仍舊記着初心嗎 不甘美麗舊回憶幻化<br />\n你記得這感動嗎 最灼眼那青春開着花<br />\n<br />\n這晚民主會結束 審議過後便會安葬<br />\n教我們賭上血肉之軀 拯救這個香港<br />\n若有神請你降福 保守我家一切平安<br />\n縱使賭注太大 未來茫茫<br />\n至少不會遺憾 終身沮喪<br />\n<br />\n過了二十年人為何 違背二十年前盛況<br />\n念記着昨日 舊情漸變燙<br />\n舊日志氣 再次耿耿於我腔<br />\n<br />\n如若退縮 他朝再度回望 可會憤慨喊著講：<br />\n「如若當晚 我有走出過來 今不必出走遠方......」<br />\n剎那再度記起當晚的眼眶<br />\n時代之中接通 閃爍了淚光<br />\n我未忘 永未忘 餘生未淡忘<br />\n<br />\n再次燃起了決心 積壓憤怒盡數釋放<br />\n無憾地賭上血肉之驅 拯救這個香港<br />\n願我們相約某天 煲底卸裝奔向榮光<br />\n縱使這個約定 路遙茫茫<br />\n這生都也會用盡氣 反抗<br />\n<br />\n重燃亮初心 有寄望~~</strong><br />\n</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n啲詞係我同班fd用咗好多心機作，原本仲諗住整埋MV + Cover 埋擺上Youtube。但小弟不才，剪片同唱歌都好垃圾，最後放棄咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果咁多位巴絲覺得啲詞寫得唔錯，可唔可以<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">幫手推上熱門，推到有Ching cover就最好</span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">[size=5]<strong>光復香港 時代革命<br />\n香港獨立 唯一出路！</strong>[/size=6]</span>"},{"pid":"d12d55839948190a8b34d58e97a77a533ab31de8","tid":2013189,"uid":302364,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T06:52:15.000Z","msg":"推到熱門有人cover(1/10)"},{"pid":"b2bf9d56d0d1811706ab74735fd7dd9a086317e4","tid":2013189,"uid":302364,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T06:52:27.000Z","msg":"推到熱門有人cover(2/10)"},{"pid":"2ad2586a38071e1a9fded876b2c933e405f0cb86","tid":2013189,"uid":302364,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T06:52:48.000Z","msg":"推到熱門有人cover<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />(3/10)"},{"pid":"64a26426ea4e6e316b2e97b3d09332665bdbf6cc","tid":2013189,"uid":302364,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T06:53:06.000Z","msg":"推到熱門有人cover<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />(4/10)"},{"pid":"beebe3c71d74f5aaa01317b6333ca283891f8350","tid":2013189,"uid":302364,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T06:53:37.000Z","msg":"到熱門有人cover<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />(5/10)"},{"pid":"639e3258ceba61cd9c6b3a6a66a579844d0c1d2e","tid":2013189,"uid":302364,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T06:53:48.000Z","msg":"到熱門有人cover<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />(6/10)"},{"pid":"0bfed47782559ee868b686f2cb441457d7e17e58","tid":2013189,"uid":302364,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T06:53:59.000Z","msg":"到熱門有人cover<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />(7/10)"},{"pid":"bbf65c811dc00d5e2498ab882e84e368e20f47fd","tid":2013189,"uid":302364,"lik